high_descs: turn left towards the wall and then right towards the table
turn right and move towards the fridge
open the fridge and put the glass cup inside
take out the glass cup from the fridge and head left towards the coffee maker
place the glass cup on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: place a cold glass cup on the coffee maker

high_descs: walk over to the kitchen counter left of the fridge
grab a white cup off of the counter
open the top fridge doors and put the cup inside, let it cool then take it out again
walk over to the left side of the kitchen counter
place the white cup under the faucet of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: get a cup ready for coffee to be poured

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter on your right.
Pick up a mug from the counter.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on your left.
Chill the mug in the fridge.
Turn around and walk to the coffee machine on the right.
Place the mug in the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled mug in a coffee machine.
